    <item>
      <title>韩国锌业因投票决定控制权而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/korea-zinc-jumps-on-report-of-vote-to-decide-battle-for-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前有媒体报道称，韩国锌业公司董事会将于周二召开会议，决定是否于下个月召开股东大会，就其最大股东提名的新董事名单进行表决，随后该公司股价飙升至涨停板。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/korea-zinc-jumps-on-report-of-vote-to-decide-battle-for-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 01:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对金砖国家货币发出警告提振美元，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/gold-slips-as-trump-s-brics-currency-warning-boosts-us-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普警告金砖国家，要求它们承诺不会创建新货币，美元上涨令金价承压，黄金价格因此下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/gold-slips-as-trump-s-brics-currency-warning-boosts-us-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 01:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南总理计划 2025 年实现经济增长率约 8%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/vietnam-pm-says-government-aims-for-8-economic-growth-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南总理范明政表示，政府将力争明年经济增长率达到 8% 左右，大幅高于议会设定的 2025 年目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/vietnam-pm-says-government-aims-for-8-economic-growth-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 01:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度债券市场有望延续涨势至 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/stars-are-aligning-for-indian-bonds-to-extend-rally-into-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度债券市场有望创下四年来最好的一年，投资者预计，在政策驱动和强劲的国内需求的推动下，印度债券市场将获得更多收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/stars-are-aligning-for-indian-bonds-to-extend-rally-into-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
