    <item>
      <title>新西兰称在蛋鸡养殖场发现的禽流感病毒并非 H5N1 毒株</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/new-zealand-says-bird-flu-found-at-egg-farm-is-not-h5n1-strain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在检测证实新西兰南部奥塔哥地区的一家商业养鸡场的鸡感染禽流感病毒后，新西兰政府已对该农场的行动实施严格的管控，但表示这种病毒株并非引起全球关注的病毒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/new-zealand-says-bird-flu-found-at-egg-farm-is-not-h5n1-strain</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 00:45:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>优衣库母公司股价因新疆言论跌至 9 周以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/fast-retailing-stock-down-most-in-9-weeks-after-xinjiang-remarks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迅销集团股价一度下跌 4.4%，为 9 月 30 日以来的最大跌幅，此前该公司董事长表示，迅销集团未使用来自新疆的棉花，随后该公司发言人表示，公司对中国的需求感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/fast-retailing-stock-down-most-in-9-weeks-after-xinjiang-remarks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 00:43:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乐天计划通过混合债券重返美元债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/rakuten-plans-return-to-dollar-bond-market-with-hybrid-notes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高收益美元票据融资成本接近 17 年来的最低水平，乐天集团 (Rakuten Group Inc.) 聘请银行发行 5 亿美元债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/rakuten-plans-return-to-dollar-bond-market-with-hybrid-notes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 00:31:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
